Subject: drm/bridge: tc358767: Simplify polling in tc_link_training()
Git-commit: aa92213f388ba88f895cc8eb432b95925b890e3b
Patch-mainline: v5.4-rc1
References: bsc#1152472

Replace explicit polling in tc_link_training() with equivalent call to
tc_poll_timeout() for simplicity. No functional change intended (not
including slightly altered debug output).

